                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120916-61-defend520 t18120916-61-punish350"></join>
               Whipped in Jail
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by a jury of half English and half foreigners, before Mr. Justice Bailey.</p>
